title: Forbes List, Benjamin Crump, NY Resolution, Sheryl Underwood, Carla's Reality Update, Supa Cent, Blacc Chyna, Closing Remarks and more.

description:
Uncle Steve gives a huge shout out to Fool #1. Big Dog makes Forbes List of Top Paid TV Hosts. The CEO has a New Years Resolution you must hear. Sheryl Underwood stops by the show to discuss Kevin Hart, Chi-Town and much more. Supa Cent makes $1 million in 90 minutes. Blacc Chyna has bleach cream that she took with her to Nigeria. In Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about probability vs possibility plus more.
